name: FSynthKnobStyle
doc: Represents the appearance of an SSynthKnob

LargeKnob: Image to use for the large knob
LargeKnobOverlay: Image to use for the dot handle
MediumKnob: Image to use for the medium large knob
MediumKnobOverlay: Image to use for the medium knob dot handle
MinValueAngle: Image to use for the medium knob dot handle
MaxValueAngle: Image to use for the medium knob dot handle
KnobSize: The size of the knobs to use.
